item.description:
a weekend version of the Thursday evening walk. I am already watching the sky in the evening and i swear it is staying lighter longer! until we can get back to our weeknight walks i thought i'd offer this one. Join us when you can for a walk around the pond. Isabelle needs to feel the "power of the pack" and she misses her friends but gets a little wild when left to her own devices! a good walk with friends and maybe a cocoa from the donut shop would do us good!

stay warm, melissa&iz
item.how_to_find_us: look for folks with dogs and talk to them!
